HEADWORD: Salable
<hw>Sal"a*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[From
<er>Sale</er>.]</ety> <def>Capable of being sold; fit to be sold;
finding a ready market.</def> -- <wordforms><wf>Sal"a*ble*ness</wf>,
<pos>n.</pos> -- <wf>Sal"a*bly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
